Package org.chronos.chronodb.internal.impl.index.querycache

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChronoIndexQueryCache
    The ChronoIndexQueryCache is used to cache the results of index queries in a ChronoDB instance.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LRUIndexQueryCache
    A simple query cache on a least-recently-used basis.
    NoIndexQueryCache
    This implementation of ChronoIndexQueryCache "fakes" a cache.
